{"tid":1054722,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想俾個驚喜女朋友 要點準備好？","createTime":"2019-03-10T05:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T06:58:29.000Z","uid":126841,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38d5475fd5042bc0f576e3ff1532d1995df32901","tid":1054722,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"我係學生黎嘅<br />\n平時放學都會去油店做part-time打發時間<br />\n屋企唔算有錢但有家族生意<br />\n有時都會幫下老豆手偷雞揸車送貨<br />\n之後學埋人地玩飛車 但自己又幾鍾意 愈玩愈上心<br />\n前幾日有個MK仔約我落場同個戰業車手玩 我應承咗<br />\n岩岩出發冇耐停係燈位等綠燈時 見到對面有個女仔好似我條女 坐喺架benz入面<br />\n之後我打俾佢問下睇下佢今晚得唔得閒<br />\n想比賽完之後約佢出黎見下面<br />\n點知原來佢仲喺鄉下準備搭火車翻嚟 話聽日先見面 <br />\n嚇得我 仲以為岩岩見到果個係佢<br />\n我打算今晚一完咗比賽就即刻過去見佢俾個surprise 想問下應該要準備d咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a142bc3d87b412f38c0461946b87afd3138f0bdc","tid":1054722,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img